name: VOXELFINE #3: "Liberty Leading the People" by Eugène Delacroix 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: This pixel art was originally made during the 4th of July weekend, 2021, since the original painting showed the July Revolution of 1830 in France. Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
